xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplayconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydeactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplaydeactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydisconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplaydisconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayfocus_event\"><code>vrdisplayfocus</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerunrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerunrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypresentchange_event\"><code>vrdisplaypresentchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">Die&nbsp;Eigenschaft WindowEventHandlers.onafterprint definiert und gibt den&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Reference/Events/onafterprint\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">onafterprint</a></code> <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> für das aktuelle Window aus.</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>window</em>.onafterprint = <em>event handling code</em>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beschreibung","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Manche Browser (inklusive Firefox 6 und neuer, Internet Explorer) senden&nbsp;<code>beforeprint&nbsp;</code>und <code>afterprint</code> Events um zu bestimmen, ob ein Druckvorgang stattgefunden hat. Diese Funktion kann genutzt werden um das User-Interface während des Druckvorgangs anzupassen (z.B das Ausblenden von User-Interface Elementen während des Druckvorgangs).</p>\n\n<p>Das&nbsp;<code>afterprint E</code>vent wird ausgelöst nachdem der Nutzer gedruckt hat oder den den Druck abgebrochen hat.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikation","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Nicht Teil einer Spezifikation.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browserkompatbilität","title":"Browserkompatbilität","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>6.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window/print\"><code>window.print</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeprint_event\"><code>window.onbeforeprint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web\">Drucken</a></li>\n <li>In Webkitbrowsern kann eine equivalentes Ergebnis mit <code>matchMedia('print')</code> erreicht werden.</li>\n <li>\n  <pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>var mediaQueryList = window.matchMedia('print');\nmediaQueryList.addListener(function(mql) {\n<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\">\t</span>if (!mql.matches) {\n<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\">\t\t</span>console.log('onafterprint');\n<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space: pre;\">\t</span>};\n});</code>\n</pre>\n </li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"grammarly-disable-indicator\" id=\"sect5\">&nbsp;</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"beschreibung"},{"text":"Spezifikation","id":"spezifikation"},{"text":"Browserkompatbilität","id":"browserkompatbilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Manche Browser (inklusive Firefox 6 und neuer, Internet Explorer) senden beforeprint und afterprint Events um zu bestimmen, ob ein Druckvorgang stattgefunden hat. Diese Funktion kann genutzt werden um das User-Interface während des Druckvorgangs anzupassen (z.B das Ausblenden von User-Interface Elementen während des Druckvorgangs).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window: afterprint event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"afterprint","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window: afterprint イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers.onafterprint","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"afterprint","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/window/afterprint_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/window/afterprint_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Window/afterprint_event","title":"WindowEventHandlers.onafterprint"}],"pageTitle":"WindowEventHandlers.onafterprint - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}